If that isn't a stupid reason I don't know what is.. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#E5E5E6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ucicelygoldenfair.showPublicProfile?language=EN>cicely goldenfair</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Lanys Cheerleader</span><br> <font color=#000033>(1/28/02 10:04:18 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylummagician.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=215.topic&index=39>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: elo</span><hr size=1> well, if that is the case, then verant has a poorly implemented dungeon design.  again, i have yet to access the third floor myself, so don't know exactly what is going on.  however, if all you need is one person to open a door and everyone can go in... then that is rather silly.<br>
